{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080540/extras/DrunkenDragon.png?t=1721862184\" /></h2> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080540/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1721862184\" /><br><br><strong>Welcome to the Drunken Dragon!</strong><br><br><strong>Step into the lively world of the Drunken Dragon Inn, where fantasy meets great cooking! In this fun tavern simulator, you are the innkeeper, managing every part of your tavern. From managing resources to mastering cooking, every decision you make helps your tavern succeed.</strong><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080540/extras/ManageResources.png?t=1721862184\" /> <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Keep your pantry full of fresh ingredients and your cellars stocked with the best ales and wines to make sure your customers are happy.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Modify your Menu to match the ingredients you have on hand</strong></li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080540/extras/CookAndCraft.png?t=1721862184\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Enjoy hands-on cooking where you pick ingredients, make meals, and cook meat on a firepit. Unlock new recipes to keep your menu interesting.</strong><br></li><li><strong>You have to work with a numerous recipes of soups and meat and also a variety of drinks.</strong></li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080540/extras/EarnAndUpgrade.png?t=1721862184\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Earn gold from happy customers and use it to improve your inn. Expand your menu, upgrade your kitchen, and make your tavern more attractive to get more important guests.</strong><br></li><li><strong>Gain ingredients.</